    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as it should, making it a dependable choice for daily commuting. While the exterior shows some minor signs of normal use, such as small stone chips, the interior remains clean and comfortable with all major features functioning properly. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that is ready for the road without needing immediate repairs.",
