    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptional vehicle, currently maintained in showroom condition. This specimen exhibits an uncompromising level of care, featuring a flawless exterior profile and an interior that remains in an original, pristine state. Every mechanical component has been rigorously vetted to ensure it meets our highest standards of performance and reliability. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the typical pre-owned category, offering the aesthetics and operational integrity of a new delivery.",
      "price": 46500.0,
