    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m finally parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This car is seriously in flawless shape\u2014it looks and drives just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, always kept it tucked away in the garage and pampered it like crazy. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup anywhere. It\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with someone who will love it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions at all!",
      "price": 43900.0,
